    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong> to a small bowl with your <strong>mint sauce</strong></p><p>Season with a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and stir it all together, then put it in the fridge until serving – this is your <strong>mint yoghurt</strong></p>",
